title: Youth unemployment rate in Egypt in 2019
summary: In general Youth unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2006 and 2007.
The highest Youth unemployment rate, of value 34.68 was reached at Year 2015
Minimum Youth unemployment rate about 24.43 was reached at Year 2010
